<body class="container mt-5 text-center">
    <div class="card d-inline-block p-5 shadow">
        <h3>Paso 1: Dinero Inicial</h3>
        <p>¿Con cuánto efectivo estás iniciando la sesión (Fondo)?</p>
        <form action="/cierre/fondo-save/<%= sessionId %>" method="POST">
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <span class="input-group-text">$</span>
                <input type="number" step="0.01" name="amount" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="0.00" autofocus required>
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg w-100">Abrir Sesión</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
